description:
A set of powerful items that revives and fully heals your entire party and restores their BP by 7.

Dragon Incense x 5
Brave Soul x 5

*These items can also be obtained in-game.
*These items can be claimed from the DLC tab on the Item page.
*If maximum capacity is exceeded, the excess is discarded.
name: Trails of Cold Steel IV: Dragon Incense Set 1
